  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307660/extras/74f7f80c6b6565b6d291239284af5b96.avif?t=1715310587\" width=659 height=67 /></span><br><br>Moving In is about relaxing in a cozy environment. You decorate the house you are moving in. There is no goal, no timer, no challenges. It is all about having a relaxing experience.  Create the house you desire. You will be able to pick up, rotate, interact and throw all the props. Most of the house utilities are interactable.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307660/extras/dbe296210a7340b0dee891222822c82c.avif?t=1715310587\" width=659 height=67 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Sandbox<br></li><li>Puzzles<br></li><li>Interactive Physics Objects<br></li><li>Move&Rotate Objects<br></li><li>Lock Objects in Place<br></li><li>Surface Snapping<br></li><li>Throw Objects<br></li><li>Cozy Houses<br></li><li>Chill Music<br></li><li>Lots of Stylized Furniture&Props<br></li><li>Save&Load System<br></li><li>Free Content Updates</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307660/extras/de8e2f66cfd78061169ac0bac7ca79e8.avif?t=1715310587\" width=659 height=67 /></span><br><br>Sandbox mode offers you a selection of houses and lots of furniture. Relax and decorate your dream house while listening to a curated chill lo-fi music playlist.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307660/extras/d6c53974a4fe37a45bf58d6888b98ff1.avif?t=1715310587\" width=659 height=67 /></span><br><br>In this mode you need to match photo references to finish the puzzles. Each puzzle will give you a different set of photos which you will need to match by placing the object in correct spots.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307660/extras/c9daf4f54d1c8559bf09528343c52819.avif?t=1715310587\" width=660 height=154 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307660/extras/74f7f80c6b6565b6d291239284af5b96.avif?t=1715310587\" width=659 height=67 /></span><br><br>Moving In is about relaxing in a cozy environment. You decorate the house you are moving in. There is no goal, no timer, no challenges. It is all about having a relaxing experience.  Create the house you desire. You will be able to pick up, rotate, interact and throw all the props. Most of the house utilities are interactable.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307660/extras/dbe296210a7340b0dee891222822c82c.avif?t=1715310587\" width=659 height=67 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Sandbox<br></li><li>Puzzles<br></li><li>Interactive Physics Objects<br></li><li>Move&Rotate Objects<br></li><li>Lock Objects in Place<br></li><li>Surface Snapping<br></li><li>Throw Objects<br></li><li>Cozy Houses<br></li><li>Chill Music<br></li><li>Lots of Stylized Furniture&Props<br></li><li>Save&Load System<br></li><li>Free Content Updates</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307660/extras/de8e2f66cfd78061169ac0bac7ca79e8.avif?t=1715310587\" width=659 height=67 /></span><br><br>Sandbox mode offers you a selection of houses and lots of furniture. Relax and decorate your dream house while listening to a curated chill lo-fi music playlist.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307660/extras/d6c53974a4fe37a45bf58d6888b98ff1.avif?t=1715310587\" width=659 height=67 /></span><br><br>In this mode you need to match photo references to finish the puzzles. Each puzzle will give you a different set of photos which you will need to match by placing the object in correct spots.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307660/extras/c9daf4f54d1c8559bf09528343c52819.avif?t=1715310587\" width=660 height=154 /></span>",
